In Reichstag tradition, as the <span style="color: #E3000F;">**SPD**</span> is the largest party, the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span> feels bound to support them.

The Reichstag agenda committee, over <span style="color: #E3000F;">**Social Democratic**</span> objections, has voted for a two-week adjournment.
